{"tid":2083150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現男朋友心入面唔係得我一個","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T20:08:55.000Z","uid":109296,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7ce7a331e093b3f89b1915f4e3b63e961ace86","tid":2083150,"uid":109296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"一齊左四年半<br />\n開始慢慢穩定 會諗同佢既將來<br />\n三年前 佢係我去exchange既時候<br />\n試過鍾意左個女同事 (無行動)<br />\n果陣覺得因為long d又有時差<br />\n我又成日去旅行 扔低佢係香港 佢先會咁<br />\n最後選擇原諒左佢<br />\n近排我又發現佢同一個女同事密密傾左幾個月Whatsapp<br />\n傾到凌晨<br />\n雖然佢唔認 話對方同佢都有另一半<br />\n先知大家唔會諗多 只係朋友關係<br />\n講既只係公事 有時講下生活上既野<br />\n係我諗多左<br />\n但我真係好痛<br />\n自問咁耐以黎 心入面只有佢一個<br />\n我呢幾年同異性 男同學 男同事都保持一條界線<br />\n⼀定唔會不停whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n佢猛咁同我對唔住<br />\n但係我過唔到自己個關<br />\n<br />\n好痛好痛"},{"pid":"20cc209e8b5d89f1b996bd5a20018db1536a7d02","tid":2083150,"uid":47480,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"男人唔到60歲真係唔好畀飽飯佢食"},{"pid":"6e0fc23452ca0aa33f7658778451a9849103be38","tid":2083150,"uid":152040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"問得預分手"},{"pid":"76a975de365b18a796ef624ef343a4430ccd9ad4","tid":2083150,"uid":83531,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"20cc209e8b5d89f1b996bd5a20018db1536a7d02","tid":2083150,"uid":47480,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"男人唔到60歲真係唔好畀飽飯佢食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db572f49e6d61bac0a5ae3c923c589fd236f0b7b","tid":2083150,"uid":340796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"介意就分開<br />\n你同佢都放唔低的話大家都會走番埋"},{"pid":"631fe64a166396454cc9691b6173b11917c6ef56","tid":2083150,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=